ring\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> ]</h4>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.unsetFieldNames\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">unsetFieldNames</span>(): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Array<string>\\\" title=\\\"array collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Array&lt;string&gt;\\\">[</a> <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> ] <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Array<string>\\\" title=\\\"array collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Array&lt;string&gt;\\\">[</a> <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> ]</h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">the name of all <a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:TypeMeta.dataFieldTypes\\\" title=\\\"method TypeMeta#dataFieldTypes\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#TypeMeta#dataFieldTypes\\\">TypeMeta#dataFieldTypes</a> on this <code>Obj</code> that <a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.isFieldSet\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#isFieldSet\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#isFieldSet\\\">are not set</a>. Array is ordered by\\nfield ordinal.</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.missingFieldNames\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">missingFieldNames</span>(): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Array<string>\\\" title=\\\"array collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Array&lt;string&gt;\\\">[</a> <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> ] <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Array<string>\\\" title=\\\"array collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Array&lt;string&gt;\\\">[</a> <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> ]</h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">the name of all <a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:TypeMeta.dataFieldTypes\\\" title=\\\"method TypeMeta#dataFieldTypes\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#TypeMeta#dataFieldTypes\\\">TypeMeta#dataFieldTypes</a> on this <code>Obj</code> that {@Link isFieldMissing are missing}. Array is ordered by\\nfield ordinal.</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.at\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">at</span>(ordinal): <em>T</em> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Return value of the field at provided ordinal. Throws an error on an invalid value (out of range).</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">ordinal</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Int32Type\\\" title=\\\"primitive int32\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Int32Type\\\">int32</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Integer ordinal of the field in the parent type</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns <em>T</em></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">value of field at ordinal</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.at-2\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">at</span>(expr, failIfNotValid): <em>T</em> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Return value for the given serialized expression</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">expr</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"serialized\\\">serialized</span><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Serialized expression to obtain the value in the given Obj</p>\\n<p class=\\\"serialized\\\">Serialized <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Expr\\\" title=\\\"type Expr\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Expr\\\">Expr</a></p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">failIfNotValid</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">If set, fails if not a valid expression</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns <em>T</em></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">value obtained as a result of expression evaluation</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.fieldValueAtPath\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">fieldValueAtPath</span>(fieldPath, failIfNotFound, context): <em>T</em> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Looks up a single field value by path from this Obj. Field paths are separated by dots so an expression like\\n<code>fieldValueAtPath(\\\"location.elevation\\\")</code> is equivalent to <code>traverse(\\\"location\\\").fieldValue(\\\"elevation\\\")</code> except\\nthat it also handles <code>null</code>. If path contains any collections then only first element will be traversed,\\nunless the collection index is specified in the path.</p>\\n<p>If you need to traverse all elements of collection fields use <a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.fieldValuesAtPath\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#fieldValuesAtPath\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#fieldValuesAtPath\\\">#fieldValuesAtPath</a> instead.</p>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">fieldPath</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"serialized\\\">serialized</span><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">field names separated by dots</p>\\n<p class=\\\"serialized\\\">Serialized <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldPath\\\" title=\\\"type FieldPath\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldPath\\\">FieldPath</a></p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">failIfNotFound</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if true, an error will be thrown if the any of the field types aren't defined</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">context</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if an error is thrown, the context returned by calling the lambda will be incorporated</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns <em>T</em></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">the field or null</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.fieldValuesAtPath\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited deprecated\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">fieldValuesAtPath</span>(fieldPath, failIfNotFound, context): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Array<T>\\\" title=\\\"array collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Array&lt;T&gt;\\\">[</a> <em>T</em> ] <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Looks up all the fields by path from root Obj. If path contains any collections then result will contain all\\ntraversals, unless the collection index is specified in the path.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"deprecated-info\\\">Deprecated: Use <a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.fieldValueAtPath\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#fieldValueAtPath\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#fieldValueAtPath\\\">#fieldValueAtPath</a> instead (final version 8.4)</p><p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">fieldPath</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"serialized\\\">serialized</span><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">field names separated by dots</p>\\n<p class=\\\"serialized\\\">Serialized <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldPath\\\" title=\\\"type FieldPath\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldPath\\\">FieldPath</a></p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">failIfNotFound</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if true, an error will be thrown if the any of the field types aren't defined</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">context</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if an error is thrown, the context returned by calling the lambda will be inc