href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Executes the specified lambda against each referenced Obj instance and replaces it's value with result of this\\nlambda application.</p>\\n<p>Result of this function call is a copy of current instance with all references replaced based on results of the\\n<code>mapper</code> invocation.</p>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">mapper</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(ft: !<a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type FieldType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldType\\\">FieldType</a>, o: !<a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a>): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">convertValue</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if true, attempt to convert the value to match the field's type</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.mapRefs-2\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">mapRefs</span>(includeEmpty, mapper, convertValue): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Executes the specified lambda against each referenced Obj instance and replaces it's value with result of this\\nlambda application.</p>\\n<p>Result of this function call is a copy of current instance with all references replaced based on results of the\\n<code>mapper</code> invocation.</p>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">includeEmpty</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if <code>true</code> will also process references with <code>null</code> / \\\"Empty\\\" references</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">mapper</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(ft: !<a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type FieldType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldType\\\">FieldType</a>, o: !<a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a>): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">function to be executed for each pair of field type and Obj instance for producing new reference value</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">convertValue</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if true, attempt to convert the value to match the field's type</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.foldFieldValues\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">foldFieldValues</span>(folder): <em>T</em> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Result of this function is application of <code>folder</code> lambda to every non empty field value where <code>accumulator</code>\\nargument is a result of previous application. Initial value of <code>accumulator</code> will be <code>null</code>.</p>\\n<p>This function is useful for calculating aggregate values based on all current non empty field values.\\nBased on the folder, may return <code>any</code> value. (Primitive, Obj, Collection, Any, etc.)\\ne.g</p>\\n<pre class=\\\"code nohighlight\\\"><code>o = {a:1, b:2, c:0}\\no.foldFieldValues((ft,value,acc) -&gt; Val.min(acc,value)) == 0 // Primitive\\n\\no = {a: {x:1, y:2}, b: {x:10, z:2}}\\no.foldFieldValues((ft,value,acc) -&gt; Val.min(acc,value)) == {x:1, y:2, z: 2} // Obj\\n</code></pre>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">folder</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(ft: !<a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type FieldType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldType\\\">FieldType</a>, value: !<a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a>, accumulator: <em>T</em>): <em>T</em> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns <em>T</em></h4>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.foldFieldValues-2\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">foldFieldValues</span>(initial, folder): <em>T</em> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Result of this function is application of <code>folder</code> lambda to every non empty field value where <code>accumulator</code>\\nargument is a result of previous application. Initial value of <code>accumulator</code> is provided via <code>initial</code> parameter.</p>\\n<p>This function is useful for calculating aggregate values based on all current non empty field values.\\nBased on the folder, may return <code>any</code> value. (Primitive, Obj, Collection, Any, etc.)\\ne.g</p>\\n<pre class=\\\"code nohighlight\\\"><code>o = {a:1, b:2, c:0}\\no.foldFieldValues((ft,value,acc) -&gt; Val.min(acc,value)) == 0 // Primitive\\n\\no = {a: {x:1, y:2}, b: {x:10, z:2}}\\no.foldFieldValues((ft,value,acc) -&gt; Val.min(acc,value)) == {x:1, y:2, z: 2} // Obj\\n</code></pre>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">initial</span>: <em>T</em>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">folder</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(ft: !<a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type FieldType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldType\\\">FieldType</a>, value: !<a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a>, accumulator: <em>T</em>): <em>T</em> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns <em>T</em></h4>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.foldFieldValues-3\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">foldFieldValues</span>(initial, spec, folder): <em>T</em> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Result of this function is application of <code>folder</code> lambda to every field value where <code>accumulator</code> argument is a\\nresult of previous application. Initial value of <code>accumulator</code> is provided via <code>initial</code> parameter.</p>\\n<p>This function is useful for calculating aggregate values based on all field values.\\nBased on the folder, may return <code>any</code> value. (Primitive, Obj, Collection, Any, etc.)\\ne.g</p>\\n<pre class=\\\"code nohighlight\\\"><code>o = {a:1, b:2, c:0}\\no.foldFieldValues((ft,value,acc) -&gt; Val.min(acc,value)) == 0 // Primitive\\n\\no = {a: {x:1, y:2}, b: {x:10, z:2}}\\no.foldFieldValues((ft,value,acc) -&gt; Val.min(acc,value)) == {x:1, y:2, z: 2} // Obj\\n</code></pre>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">initial</span>: <em>T</em>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">spec</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:ValueSpec\\\" title=\\\"type ValueSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#ValueSpec\\\">ValueSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">folder</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(ft: !<a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type