\"type ValueType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#ValueType\\\">ValueType</a>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">bindings</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Map<string,_any>\\\" title=\\\"map collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Map&lt;string, any&gt;\\\">map</a>&lt;string, <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a>&gt;\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">options</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Expr.CompileOptions\\\" title=\\\"type Expr.CompileOptions\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Expr.CompileOptions\\\">Expr.CompileOptions</a>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a></h4>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.evalProjection-2\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">evalProjection</span>(projection, bindings, options): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:JsonType\\\" title=\\\"primitive json\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#JsonType\\\">json</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Evaluates given projection over this instance and returns results as json.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">projection</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:JsonType\\\" title=\\\"primitive json\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#JsonType\\\">json</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"