-empty</span></span></h4>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withField\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">withField</span>(field, value, doNotConvert): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Builds a new Obj instance by adding the provided field in it. The name must correspond to an existing field\\ndefined on this type or its mixins. The value must be of the correct type if doNotConvert flag is true.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">field</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">name of the field</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">value</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">of the field</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">doNotConvert</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if true, do not attempt to convert the value to match the field's type</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">new Obj</p>\\n</div><div class=\\\"see\\\"><p>See:</p>\\n<ul class=\\\"see\\\">\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withoutField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#withoutField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#withoutField\\\">withoutField</a></li>\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.defaultField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#defaultField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#defaultField\\\">defaultField</a></li>\\n</ul></div>\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withField-2\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">withField</span>(field, value, doNotConvert): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Builds a new Obj instance by adding the provided field in it. The name must correspond to an existing field\\ndefined on this type or its mixins. The value must be of the correct type if doNotConvert flag is true.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">field</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type FieldType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldType\\\">FieldType</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">the field</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">value</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">of the field</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">doNotConvert</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if true, do not attempt to convert the value to match the field's type</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">new Obj</p>\\n</div><div class=\\\"see\\\"><p>See:</p>\\n<ul class=\\\"see\\\">\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withoutField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#withoutField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#withoutField\\\">withoutField</a></li>\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.defaultField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#defaultField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#defaultField\\\">defaultField</a></li>\\n</ul></div>\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withFields\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">withFields</span>(fields, doNotConvert): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Builds a new Obj instance by adding the provided fields in it. The name must correspond to an existing fields\\ndefined on this type or its mixins. The values must be of the correct type if doNotConvert flag is true.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">fields</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Map<string,_any>\\\" title=\\\"map collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Map&lt;string, any&gt;\\\">map</a>&lt;string, <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a>&gt; <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">map of field names/values</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">doNotConvert</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if true, attempt to convert the values to match the fields' type</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">new Obj</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withFieldAtPath\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">withFieldAtPath</span>(path, value, doNotConvert, doNotCreateIfMissing): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Builds a new Obj with the value at the specified path field. If the field is null, the field <a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.isFieldSet\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#isFieldSet\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#isFieldSet\\\">#isFieldSet</a> to null.\\nIf you would like to <a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.unsetField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#unsetField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#unsetField\\\">#unsetField</a>, you should call <a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withoutFieldAtPath\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#withoutFieldAtPath\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#withoutFieldAtPath\\\">#withoutFieldAtPath</a> instead.</p>\\n<p>Immutable objects may return the same instance if the field being set does not actually represent a\\nchange to the existing object.</p>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">path</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">path to set value at</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">value</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">value to set</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">doNotConvert</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if true, attempt to convert the values to match the fields' type</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">doNotCreateIfMissing</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">true indicates that any empty reference along the path will not set the value</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">new Obj</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withoutFieldAtPath\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">withoutFieldAtPath</span>(path): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Builds a new Obj without the specified path field.</p>\\n<p>Immutable objects may return the same instance if the field being removed does not actually represent a\\nchange to the existing object.</p>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">path</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">path for field to remove</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">new Obj</p>\\n</div><div class=\\\"see\\\"><p>See:</p>\\n<ul class=\\\"see\\\">\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withFieldAtPath\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#withFieldAtPath\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#withFieldAtPath\\\">withFieldAtPath</a></li>\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withoutField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#withoutField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#withoutField\\\">withoutField</a></li>\\n</ul></div>\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withoutField\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">withoutField</span>(field): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Builds a new Obj, removing the field with the provided name.</p>\\n<p>Immutable objects may return the same instance if the field being removed is not present in the existing object.</p>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">field</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">name of the field to remove</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">new Obj with removed field</p>\\n</div><div class=\\\"see\\\"><p>See:</p>\\n<ul class=\\\"see\\\">\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.unsetField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#unsetField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#unsetField\\\">unsetField</a></li>\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.removeField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#removeField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#removeField\\\">removeField</a></li>\\n</ul></div>\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withoutField-2\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">withoutField</span>(field): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Builds a new Obj, removing the field with the provided field type.</p>\\n<p>Immutable objects may return the same instance if the field being removed is not present in the existing object.</p>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">field</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type FieldType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldType\\\">FieldType</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">name of the field to remove</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">new Obj with removed field</p>\\n</div><div class=\\\"see\\\"><p>See:</p>\\n<ul class=\\\"see\\\">\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.unsetField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#unsetField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#unsetField\\\">unsetField</a></li>\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.removeField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#removeField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#removeField\\\">removeField</a></li>\\n</ul></div>\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withoutFields\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">withoutFields</span>(fields): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Builds a new Obj, removing the fields with the provided names.</p>\\n<p>Immutable objects may return the same instance if the fields being removed are not present in the existing object.</p>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">fields</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Array<string>\\\" title=\\\"array collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Array&lt;string&gt;\\\">[</a> <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> ] <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">names of the fields to remove</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">new Obj with removed fields</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withoutFieldsByType\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">withoutFieldsByType</span>(fields): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Builds a new Obj, removing the fields with the provided field types. Be sure to use the FieldType instance for the\\nexact same type as the type of the obj to respect the \\\"ordinal\\\" of the field type</p>\\n<p>Immutable objects may return the same instance if the fields being removed are not present in the existing object.</p>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">fields</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Array<FieldType>\\\" title=\\\"array collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Array&lt;FieldType&gt;\\\">[</a> <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type FieldType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldType\\\">FieldType</a> ] <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">field types to remove</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">new Obj with removed fields</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withoutSecretFields\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">withoutSecretFields</span>(): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">a new Obj, removing the field types marked with annotation @config(secret=true) recursively</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.secretFieldsSet\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">secretFieldsSet</span>(): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Array<string>\\\" title=\\\"array collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Array&lt;string&gt;\\\">[</a> <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> ] <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Array<string>\\\" title=\\\"array collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Array&lt;string&gt;\\\">[</a> <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> ] <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">a list of the secret field paths that were found to be set on this Obj.</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withDefaults\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">withDefaults</span>(includeEmptyRefsWithDefaults, defaultFields): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Builds a new Obj instance by adding the default values (if defined) for all unset fields. This is implemented by\\ncalling <a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FieldType.defaultValue\\\" title=\\\"method FieldType#defaultValue\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FieldType#defaultValue\\\">defaultValue</a> for a field if it is not already set and\\n<a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FieldType.hasDefault\\\" title=\\\"method FieldType#hasDefault\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FieldType#hasDefault\\\">has a default</a>. It will also set {@see <a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:ValueType.initialValue\\\" title=\\\"method ValueType#initialValue\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#ValueType#initialValue\\\">ValueType#initialValue</a> initial values} for\\nfields with required primitive ValueTypes (E.g. x: <code>!int32</code> -&gt; will be set to 0). Note that this will not overwrite\\nfields that have already been set.</p>\\n<p><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FunctionParam.validateArg\\\" title=\\\"method FunctionParam#validateArg\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FunctionParam#validateArg\\\">FunctionParam#validateArg</a> will call <a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.withDefaults\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#withDefaults\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#withDefaults\\\">#withDefaults</a> for <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Spec\\\" title=\\\"type Spec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Spec\\\">Spec</a>s passed as arguments to methods.\\nAs a result, methods should be implemented assuming all default values are set on <code>Spec</code> arguments.</p>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">includeEmptyRefsWithDefaults</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">it <code>true</code> then missing / empty child references that have fields with defaults will also be instantiated</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">defaultFields</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Array<string>\\\" title=\\\"array collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Array&lt;string&gt;\\\">[</a> <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> ]\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">If not empty, a list of default field paths to populate.  Any default fields not specified in the\\narray will be ignored.</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">new Obj</p>\\n</div><div class=\\\"see\\\"><p>See:</p>\\n<ul class=\\\"see\\\">\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.defaultField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#defaultField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#defaultField\\\">defaultField</a></li>\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FieldType.defaultValueConst\\\" title=\\\"method FieldType#defaultValueConst\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FieldType#defaultValueConst\\\">FieldType#defaultValueConst</a></li>\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FieldType.defaultValue\\\" title=\\\"method FieldType#defaultValue\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FieldType#defaultValue\\\">FieldType#defaultValue</a></li>\\n</ul></div>\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.defaultField\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">defaultField</span>(field): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Builds a new Obj, by setting a field on this <code>Obj</code> to the field's default value. If the field has no default, this\\nmethod will behave the same as <a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.unsetField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchSpec#unsetField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchSpec#unsetField\\\">#unsetField</a>.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"i