e:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a>&gt;\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">mapping of fields of the object to the respective merge annotations</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">the new merged Obj</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.mergeObj-2\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">mergeObj</span>(other, otherFieldsFilter): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Merges all the fields of the provided Obj into this instance, producing a new Obj of the same type as this one.\\nIn case of conflicts, fields of other instance take precedence.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">other</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">object</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">otherFieldsFilter</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Type\\\" title=\\\"type Type\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Type\\\">Type</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">only fields of otherFieldsFilter type from other are merged into this obj.</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">the new merged Obj</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.mergeObj-3\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">mergeObj</span>(other, deep, merger): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Merge the fields of this Obj with corresponding fields on other Obj using the provided lambda. This means that\\nfields that exist on other Obj and do not exist on this Obj will not be added to final Obj.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">other</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">deep</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if set to true then traverse reference and collection fields and merge corresponding fields or elements with\\nthe same key or index.</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">merger</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(fp: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldPath\\\" title=\\\"type FieldPath\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldPath\\\">FieldPath</a>, v: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a>, otherFp: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldPath\\\" title=\\\"type FieldPath\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldPath\\\">FieldPath</a>, otherV: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a>): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.mergeObj-4\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">mergeObj</span>(other, merger): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Merge the fields of this Obj with corresponding fields on other Obj using the provided lambda. This means that\\nfields that exist other Obj and do not exist on this Obj will not be added to final Obj or evaluated. Does not\\ntraverse child reference and collection fields.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">other</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">merger</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(ft: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type FieldType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldType\\\">FieldType</a>, v: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a>, otherFt: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type FieldType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldType\\\">FieldType</a>, otherV: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a>): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.mergeAndExpandObj\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">mergeAndExpandObj</span>(other, merger): <em>R</em>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Create new Obj with all non-null fields of this and other. Fields that are non null in both apply merger lambda.\\nFields that non null in only one of this and other will be in the resulting Obj without change.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">other</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">merger</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(ft: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type FieldType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldType\\\">FieldType</a>, v: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a>, otherFt: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type FieldType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldType\\\">FieldType</a>, otherV: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a>): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns <em>R</em>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></h4>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.mergeJson\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">mergeJson</span>(json): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">json</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:JsonType\\\" title=\\\"primitive json\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#JsonType\\\">json</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.mergeChildren\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">mergeChildren</span>(deep, objKey, filter): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Merge the obj references within the current obj</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">deep</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">If set, traverses the reference fields within the obj as well for a deep merge</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">objKey</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(child: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a>): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">lambda specifying how to obtain the key for the Obj while determining which Objs to merge</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">filter</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(fieldPath: !<a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a>): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"serialized\\\">serialized</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Field paths that need to be filtered from this merge</p>\\n<p class=\\\"serialized\\\">Serialized <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldPath\\\" title=\\\"type FieldPath\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldPath\\\">FieldPath</a></p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Obj with child references merged</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.sumObj\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">sumObj</span>(other, deep): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Adds the numeric Obj fields with the other Objs respective fields.\\nIf deep is set it will traverse reference and collection fields and sum corresponding numeric fields in\\nreferences with same name and collection elements at same index or key.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">other</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">deep</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchSpec.singletonArray\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">singletonArray</span>(): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Array<mixing_FetchSpec>\\\" title=\\\"array collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Array&lt;mixing FetchSpec&gt;\\\">[</a> mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> ] <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Build an array of the correct type with a single element which is this instance.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Array<mixing_FetchSpec>\\\" title=\\\"array collection\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Array&lt;mixing FetchSpec&gt;\\\">[</a> mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchSpec\\\" title=\\\"type FetchSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchSpec\\\">FetchSpec</a> ] <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span c