n class=\\\"name\\\">action</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(ft: !<a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type FieldType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldType\\\">FieldType</a>, value: native) <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">lambda to apply</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:Filter.eachFieldValueWhile\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">eachFieldValueWhile</span>(spec, action): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Perform an action for each field of this object while processing action returns <code>true</code>. Fields are filtered based\\non provided <code>spec</code>.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">spec</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:ValueSpec\\\" title=\\\"type ValueSpec\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#ValueSpec\\\">ValueSpec</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">which fields to include</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">action</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#T