er</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">Result of this function call is a copy of current instance with specified field value replaced based on result of\\nthe <code>mapper</code> invocation.</p>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">field</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FieldType\\\" title=\\\"type FieldType\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FieldType\\\">FieldType</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">field being mapped</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">includeEmpty</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if set, invokes mapper for fields with empty value</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">mapper</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:LambdaType\\\" title=\\\"lambda\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#LambdaType\\\">lambda</a>(value: !<a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a>): <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">lambda to apply for every field value to produce a new value for that field</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">convertValue</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\"