d:FetchResult.unsetField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchResult#unsetField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchResult#unsetField\\\">#unsetField</a>, you should call <a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchResult.withoutFieldAtPath\\\" title=\\\"method FetchResult#withoutFieldAtPath\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchResult#withoutFieldAtPath\\\">#withoutFieldAtPath</a> instead.</p>\\n<p>Immutable objects may return the same instance if the field being set does not actually represent a\\nchange to the existing object.</p>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">path</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">path to set value at</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">value</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:AnyType\\\" title=\\\"any\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#AnyType\\\">any</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">value to set</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">doNotConvert</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">if true, attempt to convert the values to match the fields' type</p>\\n</li>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter optional\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">doNotCreateIfMissing</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:BooleanType\\\" title=\\\"primitive boolean\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#BooleanType\\\">boolean</a>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">true indicates that any empty reference along the path will not set the value</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchResult\\\" title=\\\"type FetchResult\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchResult\\\">FetchResult</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">new Obj</p>\\n</div></div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchResult.withoutFieldAtPath\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">withoutFieldAtPath</span>(path): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchResult\\\" title=\\\"type FetchResult\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchResult\\\">FetchResult</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Builds a new Obj without the specified path field.</p>\\n<p>Immutable objects may return the same instance if the field being removed does not actually represent a\\nchange to the existing object.</p>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">path</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType\\\" title=\\\"primitive string\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#StringType\\\">string</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"required\\\">required</span><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">path for field to remove</p>\\n</li>\\n</ol></div>\\n<div class=\\\"returns\\\"><h4>Returns mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchResult\\\" title=\\\"type FetchResult\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchResult\\\">FetchResult</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"non-empty\\\">non-empty</span></span></h4>\\n<p class=\\\"description\\\">new Obj</p>\\n</div><div class=\\\"see\\\"><p>See:</p>\\n<ul class=\\\"see\\\">\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchResult.withFieldAtPath\\\" title=\\\"method FetchResult#withFieldAtPath\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchResult#withFieldAtPath\\\">withFieldAtPath</a></li>\\n<li class=\\\"see\\\"><a class=\\\"method documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"method:FetchResult.withoutField\\\" title=\\\"method FetchResult#withoutField\\\" href=\\\"#METHOD#FetchResult#withoutField\\\">withoutField</a></li>\\n</ul></div>\\n</div>\\n<div id=\\\"method:FetchResult.withoutField\\\" class=\\\"structure method inherited\\\">\\n<h3><span class=\\\"name\\\">withoutField</span>(field): mixing <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:FetchResult\\\" title=\\\"type FetchResult\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#FetchResult\\\">FetchResult</a> <span class=\\\"attributes\\\"><span class=\\\"member\\\">member</span><span class=\\\"overloaded\\\">overloaded</span><span class=\\\"final\\\">final</span><span class=\\\"inherited\\\">inherited</span></span></h3>\\n<div class=\\\"description\\\">\\n<p>Builds a new Obj, removing the field with the provided name.</p>\\n<p>Immutable objects may return the same instance if the field being removed is not present in the existing object.</p>\\n</div>\\n<p class=\\\"inherited-from\\\">Inherited from <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:Obj\\\" title=\\\"type Obj\\\" href=\\\"#TYPE#Obj\\\">Obj</a></p>\\n<div class=\\\"parameters\\\"><h4>Parameters:</h4>\\n<ol>\\n<li class=\\\"parameter required\\\"><span class=\\\"name\\\">field</span>: <a class=\\\"type documentation\\\" data-to-id=\\\"type:StringType